Here's what I know:<br>
Imps and Fire elementals in Lavastorm<br>
All Elemental  (Najena, Large Water Elemental (lguk))<br>
Not many other places with elemental I know of.<br>
Imps in Solsek B, but I have heard no one hunts these guys cuz they are very hard, only time you kill them is on a efreeti run, no idea if true, never hunted in solb<br>
Gargoryoles(sp?) Mistmoore, OOT, lguk<br>
Shadowmen SK, WC, Lesser Faydark<br>
<br>
can't think of any others right now.<br>
